<HEADLINE>
ASIA'S SHIFTING BALANCE PROMISES TRICKY TIMES AHEAD  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 925-word material from The New York
