QUIPS, QUIRKS AND QUOTES FROM THIS WEEK'S CAMPAIGN TRAIL  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Political, Humor Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 325-word material from The New York
