<HEADLINE>
CANADA'S NOT-SO-FRIENDLY SKIES  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Business Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 625-word material from The New York
Times Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist.
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
