<P>
   RETREATS _ Spiritual retreats. Trips to Israel and other holy
sites in the Mid-East. Volunteer projects to help the needy. These
are some of the ways people in metro Atlanta spent the summer. We
detail. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution) WITH PHOTOS.
