   CHURCH-SCHOOL _ Church schools are gearing up for fall. They
promise kids enlightening spiritual lessons. But most parents are
completely in the dark about them. Sunday schools are arguably one
of the most formative experiences in a youngster's life. And most
parents haven't a clue what goes on inside those classrooms.
(Gushee, Palm Beach Post).
