   COXNET HEALTHY LIVING 0829 -- The standard of beauty in many
cultures has become smooth and essentially hairless. Oh, we'll
tolerate some hair, but only on the right places: heads, for
example, or Tom Selleck's chest. Otherwise, there are many ways to
remove it, from waxing to lasers to photo-epilation. (Saur, Grand
