   HIGH-TECH BLASTING NEEDED TO TOPPLE SEATTLE'S KINGDOME &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   TOPPLE-SEATTLE'S-KINGDOME-POPMECH _ Builders of Seattle's
Kingdome said it was strong enough to last a millennium. But when
it the sports arena was deemed obsolete, it took demolition experts
a scant 16.8 seconds to turn the world's largest thin-shell
concrete dome into a cloud of dust and debris. Here's how they did
it. (800 words.) By Tom Paulson.
