   ILL-RICHES-SCHEME (Mattoon, Ill.) _ For a few years, residents
here wondered how average people were suddenly getting rich.
Federal prosecutors say they have the answer: 11 Mattoon residents
and eight others have been indicted in a $12.5 million
international Ponzi scheme orchestrated by a retired electrician
from Mattoon. By Pam Belluck.
</P>
