<P>
   MEXICO-ZEDILLO _ MEXICO CITY _ Mexican President Ernesto Zedillo
is scheduled to give his final state of the union address Friday
night in which he's expected to discuss the first election to
result in a loss for his Institutiuonal Revoluitonary Party, or the
PRI. Developing. (Ferriss, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   EDs: An early version is expected to move on the NYT wire by 6
p.m. EDT; the final version following speech by 10:30 p.m. EDT.
</P>
<P>
   COSTARICA-ECOTOURISM _ PUNTARENAS, Costa Rica _ Costa Rica is
considered one of the pioneers in eco-tourism, luring visitors to
hike its tropical rainforests, raft its raging mountain rivers, and
trek through its high mountain cloud forests. We profile the rich
offerings. Developing. (Williams, Cox News Service).
</P>
