<P>
   AOL _ WASHINGTON _ The CEOs of Time Warner and America Online
will testify this month before the House Commerce subcommittee on
telecommunications, trade and consumer protection. Both in the U.S.
and Europe, government officials are taking a hard look at this
merger. (Geewax, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   WAN: Location Atlanta, category Business, subcategory
