   SHARP DRIVING _ Unless you have been under a rock or on a
deserted tropical island, you have heard of Firestone's tire
recall. Hopefully, regardless of what brand of tire your vehicle
wears, you have heeded warnings to maintain the proper air
pressure. (Sharp, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). Includes 1-column
