   COXNET INSIDE NASCAR 0901: HOT WALLACE _ The swagger is back for
Rusty Wallace, winner of last week's Goracing.com500. So is the
smile and the cockiness. Wallace is the hottest driver in the
Winston Cup Series, winning three of the last five races and
finishing second at Indianapolis. He isn't the points leader, but
he's the center of attention around the track these days. (Carvell,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
