<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    U.S., EUROPEAN SCRUTINY GROWING OVER AOL-TIME WARNER MERGER
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
