<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-01 17:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8702 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u k BC-HELEN-THOMAS-HNS &LR;      09-01 0905
