<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-MISSILE (Washington) _ President Clinton says the United
States will continue researching national missile defense, but he
delays a decision on deployment until the next administration. By
John Donnelly. 1200 words.
</P>
