<P>
   GORE-DETAILS (Washington) _ On the campaign trail, Al Gore is
following his ``details'' strategy, an effort to contrast his
gravitas with George W. Bush's. By reeling off details _ many of
which voters aren't listening to or can't understand _ Gore is
betting that his wonky side will overcome Bush's charm. By Anne E.
Kornblut. 1300 words.
