</P>
<P>
   ARAB-PROFILING (Undated) _ A growing number of Muslims are
calling on the FAA to stop what they call airport profiling. The
FAA is preparing a $1.5 million study to determine if
Arab-Americans are being unfairly targeted in security checks. By
Cindy Rodriguez. 900 words. (a and i coding)
</P>
<P>
   MA-DRUG-USE (Boston) _ Blame it on the hippies. Or the liberals.
Or the college kids. Or the New Agers. Or the New York drug
dealers. The theories about why Massachusetts has such high drug
and alcohol use run the gamut. By Richard Saltus and Raja Mishra.
1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   HEMLOCK-MEETS (Boston) _ The controversial Hemlock Society is
co-sponsoring the World Assisted Dying Conference in Boston this
weekend, to the chagrin of groups representing Catholics and
disabled people. By Anne Barnard. 900 words.
</P>
