</P>
<P>
   FBN-PATRIOTS (Foxborough, Mass.) _ Otis Smith was plucked off
the waiver wire by Bill Belichick for a purpose, that being Smith
knows his defensive system, understands how to be a role player and
what he adds in terms of leadership to the team might be his
largest attribute. By Nick Cafardo. 950 words.
</P>
<P>
