   JOBSHARING _ Job sharing is a creative solution to balancing
work/life responsibilities _ and in attracting and retaining
talented employees. A recent survey by the Society for Human
Resource Management shows that 22 percent of the companies studied
offer job-sharing. Experts expect the option to grow. We'll look a
the trend and sort out how job sharing works. (Mallory, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) WITH ILLUSTRATION
