<P>
   FBN-CHANDLER _ ATLANTA _ Much of the offseason focus on the
Falcons has been on the recovery from injury and surgery of Jamal
Anderson, but Chris Chandler is also a key. When healthy, Chandler
is among best QBs in the NFL, but he missed four games last season
and parts of four others with injuries. Can he remain healthy
enough to help the Falcons try to recover enough to make the
playoffs? (Winkeljohn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
