<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Saturday, Sept. 2. The night supervisor for The New York
Times News Service is Pat Ryan; phone: 888-346-9867 or
212-556-1927; e-mail: patryan(at)nytimes.com.
