<HEADLINE>
MARKET INSIGHT: BUMPER CROP FROM THE MIDDLE GROUND 
</HEADLINE>
   (For release Sunday, Sept. 3)  
 By KENNETH N. GILPIN   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
