<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-01 20:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8883 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f BC-MEA-CULPA-ADS-$ADV03-     09-01 1110
