<HEADLINE>
CLINTON TO LEAVE DECISION ON MISSILE SHIELD TO HIS SUCCESSOR 
</HEADLINE>
   (SUBS to rewrite with new reporting; expands by 1100 words; story
is now two takes. note single byline.)  
(EDS NOTE: The complete text of President Clinton's speech is
available from The New York Times on the Web: www.nytimes.com) (ART
